name: Cosmic Goat Yogurt
description: For are Cosmic Goat Yogurt, we import 23 different types of fruit from the farthest regions of the Milky Way. The fruit is mashed together and then fermented for 23 days. After the fermentation is complete, we mix the fruit paste with goat yogurt made from the milk of 23 goats. Our Cosmic Goat Yogurt is a strong psychoactive nootropic, with life altering effects/consequences. There is a limit of one bowl per lifetime.
